urdu transliteration text:
@HujjatELC
Jab Aun O Muhammad Nay Maula Ko Bulaya Ho Ga
Masooma Kee Lashon Pe Akbar Ka Baba Janay, Kis Haal Mai Aaya Ho Ga

@HujjatELC
Sadqa Hai Aun O Mohammad, Akbar Aur Ali Asghar KaDo Baiton Kee Lashon Pe Ye Soch Ke Maa Ujri Ne, Na Ashk Bahaya Ho Ga
Aun and Muhammad have sacrificed themselves before Ali Akbar & Asghar,
